---
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import { ClientRouter } from 'astro:transitions';

const siteTitle = "Web Design Limassol | Professional Website Development in Limassol, Cyprus";
const siteDescription = "Looking for web design in Limassol? We create stunning, affordable websites for businesses in Limassol. Local web designer with proven results. Get a free quote today.";
const siteUrl = "https://cypruswebdesign.com";
const siteName = "Cyprus Web Design";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />

		<title>{siteTitle}</title>
		<meta name="title" content={siteTitle} />
		<meta name="description" content={siteDescription} />
		<meta name="keywords" content="web design limassol, website design limassol, web developer limassol, limassol web designer, website development limassol, affordable web design limassol, professional website limassol, e-commerce limassol, SEO limassol" />
		<meta name="author" content={siteName} />
		<meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />

		<link rel="canonical" href={`${siteUrl}/web-design-limassol`} />

		<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
		<meta property="og:url" content={`${siteUrl}/web-design-limassol`} />
		<meta property="og:title" content={siteTitle} />
		<meta property="og:description" content={siteDescription} />
		<meta property="og:image" content={`${siteUrl}/og-image.jpg`} />
		<meta property="og:site_name" content={siteName} />

		<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
		<meta name="twitter:title" content={siteTitle} />
		<meta name="twitter:description" content={siteDescription} />

		<meta name="geo.region" content="CY-06" />
		<meta name="geo.placename" content="Limassol" />
		<meta name="geo.position" content="34.6786;33.0413" />

		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<ClientRouter />

		<script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
		{
			"@context": "https://schema.org",
			"@type": "LocalBusiness",
			"name": "Cyprus Web Design - Limassol",
			"description": "Professional web design and development services in Limassol, Cyprus. We create beautiful, functional websites for local businesses.",
			"url": "https://cypruswebdesign.com/web-design-limassol",
			"telephone": "+357-00-000000",
			"email": "info@cypruswebdesign.com",
			"address": {
				"@type": "PostalAddress",
				"addressLocality": "Limassol",
				"addressRegion": "Limassol",
				"addressCountry": "CY"
			},
			"geo": {
				"@type": "GeoCoordinates",
				"latitude": "34.6786",
				"longitude": "33.0413"
			},
			"areaServed": {
				"@type": "City",
				"name": "Limassol"
			},
			"serviceType": [
				"Web Design",
				"Web Development",
				"E-commerce Development",
				"SEO Services"
			],
			"priceRange": "$$"
		}
		</script>

		<style>
			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			html {
				scroll-behavior: smooth;
			}

			body {
				font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
				background: #e8e6e3;
				color: #1e293b;
				min-height: 100vh;
				position: relative;
				overflow-x: hidden;
			}

			.dappled-light {
				position: fixed;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				pointer-events: none;
				z-index: 0;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.dappled-light::before {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				top: -50%;
				right: -20%;
				width: 150%;
				height: 200%;
				background:
					repeating-linear-gradient(
						-55deg,
						transparent 0px,
						transparent 80px,
						rgba(255,255,255,0.7) 80px,
						rgba(255,255,255,0.7) 120px,
						transparent 120px,
						transparent 200px
					);
				filter: blur(40px);
				opacity: 0.6;
			}

			.dappled-light::after {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 40%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 100%);
			}

			.main-content {
				position: relative;
				z-index: 1;
				padding: 80px 120px 80px 200px;
				max-width: 1000px;
			}

			.page-title {
				font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
				font-size: 3rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				line-height: 1.1;
				color: #2d3748;
				margin-bottom: 16px;
				letter-spacing: -0.02em;
			}

			.page-subtitle {
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				color: #4a5568;
				margin-bottom: 48px;
				max-width: 600px;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			.content-section {
				margin-bottom: 48px;
			}

			.content-section p {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
				color: #4a5568;
				margin-bottom: 24px;
				max-width: 700px;
			}

			.section-title {
				font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
				font-size: 1.8rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: #2d3748;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				margin-top: 48px;
			}

			.section-title:first-of-type {
				margin-top: 0;
			}

			/* Services Grid */
			.services-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
				gap: 24px;
				margin-bottom: 48px;
			}

			.service-card {
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
				border-radius: 16px;
				padding: 28px;
				border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
			}

			.service-card h3 {
				font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: #2d3748;
				margin-bottom: 12px;
			}

			.service-card p {
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #4a5568;
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}

			/* Why Limassol Section */
			.benefits-list {
				list-style: none;
				margin-bottom: 32px;
			}

			.benefits-list li {
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				line-height: 1.7;
				color: #4a5568;
				padding: 12px 0;
				padding-left: 28px;
				position: relative;
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
			}

			.benefits-list li:last-child {
				border-bottom: none;
			}

			.benefits-list li::before {
				content: '✓';
				position: absolute;
				left: 0;
				color: #48bb78;
				font-weight: 600;
			}

			/* Areas We Serve */
			.areas-grid {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 12px;
				margin-bottom: 32px;
			}

			.area-tag {
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
				padding: 8px 16px;
				border-radius: 20px;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: #4a5568;
				border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
			}

			/* CTA Section */
			.cta-section {
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
				border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
				border-radius: 16px;
				padding: 40px;
				margin-top: 48px;
				margin-bottom: 48px;
			}

			.cta-section h2 {
				font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
				font-size: 1.6rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: #2d3748;
				margin-bottom: 16px;
			}

			.cta-section p {
				color: #4a5568;
				margin-bottom: 24px;
				max-width: 500px;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			.cta-button {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 14px 28px;
				background: #2d3748;
				color: #fff;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 8px;
				font-weight: 600;
				transition: all 0.2s ease;
			}

			.cta-button:hover {
				background: #1a202c;
				transform: translateY(-2px);
			}

			.back-link {
				display: inline-block;
				color: #4299e1;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.back-link:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}

			/* FAQ Section */
			.faq-section {
				margin-top: 48px;
			}

			.faq-item {
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 24px;
				margin-bottom: 16px;
			}

			.faq-question {
				font-weight: 600;
				color: #2d3748;
				margin-bottom: 12px;
				font-size: 1.1rem;
			}

			.faq-answer {
				color: #4a5568;
				line-height: 1.7;
			}

			/* Dark mode */
			html.dark body {
				background: #1a1a2e;
				color: #e2e8f0;
			}

			html.dark .dappled-light::before {
				background:
					repeating-linear-gradient(
						-55deg,
						transparent 0px,
						transparent 80px,
						rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 80px,
						rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 120px,
						transparent 120px,
						transparent 200px
					);
				opacity: 0.3;
			}

			html.dark .dappled-light::after {
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 40%, rgba(100, 100, 150, 0.1) 100%);
			}

			html.dark .page-title,
			html.dark .section-title,
			html.dark .service-card h3,
			html.dark .cta-section h2,
			html.dark .faq-question {
				color: #e2e8f0;
			}

			html.dark .page-subtitle,
			html.dark .content-section p,
			html.dark .service-card p,
			html.dark .benefits-list li,
			html.dark .cta-section p,
			html.dark .faq-answer {
				color: #a0aec0;
			}

			html.dark .service-card,
			html.dark .cta-section,
			html.dark .faq-item {
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
				border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
			}

			html.dark .area-tag {
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
				border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
				color: #a0aec0;
			}

			html.dark .benefits-list li {
				border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
			}

			html.dark .cta-button {
				background: #e2e8f0;
				color: #1a1a2e;
			}

			html.dark .cta-button:hover {
				background: #fff;
			}

			html.dark .back-link {
				color: #63b3ed;
			}

			/* Responsive */
			@media (max-width: 1024px) {
				.main-content {
					padding: 100px 60px 60px 60px;
				}

				.services-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
			}

			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.main-content {
					padding: 100px 24px 60px 24px;
				}

				.page-title {
					font-size: 2.2rem;
				}

				.section-title {
					font-size: 1.5rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="dappled-light"></div>
		<Navbar />

		<main class="main-content">
			<h1 class="page-title">Web Design in Limassol</h1>
			<p class="page-subtitle">Professional website design and development for businesses in Limassol, Cyprus. Local expertise, global standards.</p>

			<div class="content-section">
				<p>
					Looking for a <strong>web designer in Limassol</strong>? You've come to the right place. We're a local
					web design agency that understands the Limassol business community. From the bustling tourist areas
					along the coast to the commercial heart of the city, we've helped businesses of all sizes establish
					their online presence.
				</p>

				<p>
					Limassol is Cyprus's business hub — home to international companies, thriving tourism, and a growing
					tech scene. Your website needs to reflect that energy and professionalism. We create websites that
					not only look great but actually help you attract customers and grow your business.
				</p>
			</div>

			<h2 class="section-title">Our Web Design Services in Limassol</h2>

			<div class="services-grid">
				<div class="service-card">
					<h3>Business Websites</h3>
					<p>Professional websites for Limassol businesses — from law firms and accounting offices to restaurants and retail shops. We create sites that build trust and convert visitors.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card">
					<h3>E-commerce & Online Stores</h3>
					<p>Sell your products online with a custom e-commerce website. Perfect for Limassol shops looking to reach customers across Cyprus and beyond.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card">
					<h3>Tourism & Hospitality</h3>
					<p>Websites for hotels, villas, tour operators, and restaurants. We know what tourists searching for Limassol experiences are looking for.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card">
					<h3>Real Estate Websites</h3>
					<p>Property listing websites for Limassol real estate agents. Showcase properties beautifully and capture leads effectively.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h2 class="section-title">Why Choose a Local Limassol Web Designer?</h2>

			<ul class="benefits-list">
				<li><strong>We understand the local market:</strong> We know Limassol businesses and what their customers expect</li>
				<li><strong>Face-to-face meetings:</strong> We're here in Limassol — we can meet in person to discuss your project</li>
				<li><strong>Local SEO expertise:</strong> We know how to help your business rank for "Limassol" searches</li>
				<li><strong>Quick support:</strong> Same timezone, same city — we're always available when you need us</li>
				<li><strong>Network connections:</strong> We can recommend trusted local photographers, copywriters, and other professionals</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="section-title">Areas We Serve in Limassol</h2>
			<p style="color: #4a5568; margin-bottom: 20px;">We work with businesses throughout the Limassol district:</p>

			<div class="areas-grid">
				<span class="area-tag">Limassol City Centre</span>
				<span class="area-tag">Tourist Area</span>
				<span class="area-tag">Old Port</span>
				<span class="area-tag">Germasogeia</span>
				<span class="area-tag">Agios Tychonas</span>
				<span class="area-tag">Amathus</span>
				<span class="area-tag">Zakaki</span>
				<span class="area-tag">Mesa Geitonia</span>
				<span class="area-tag">Kapsalos</span>
				<span class="area-tag">Polemidia</span>
				<span class="area-tag">Columbia</span>
				<span class="area-tag">Agios Athanasios</span>
			</div>

			<h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

			<div class="faq-section">
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">How much does a website cost in Limassol?</h3>
					<p class="faq-answer">
						Our website packages start from €500 for a simple business site. Most Limassol businesses
						choose our Business package at €1,200 which includes custom design, SEO optimization, and
						ongoing support. <a href="/prices" style="color: #4299e1;">View our full pricing</a>.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">Can we meet in person to discuss my project?</h3>
					<p class="faq-answer">
						Absolutely! We're based in Limassol and happy to meet at your office, a local café, or our
						workspace. We find that face-to-face meetings help us better understand your business and
						create a website that truly fits your needs.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">How long does it take to build a website?</h3>
					<p class="faq-answer">
						A typical business website takes 2-3 weeks from start to finish. If you need something
						faster, we can often accommodate rush projects. E-commerce sites and more complex projects
						may take 3-4 weeks.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">Will my website show up when people search for businesses in Limassol?</h3>
					<p class="faq-answer">
						Yes! We optimize every website for local search. This includes setting up your Google Business
						Profile, adding location-specific content, and implementing technical SEO best practices.
						Our goal is to help you rank for searches like "your service + Limassol."
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-section">
				<h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
				<p>
					Let's discuss your project over a coffee. We'll give you honest advice about what you need
					(and what you don't) — no pressure, no obligation.
				</p>
				<a href="mailto:info@cypruswebdesign.com?subject=Web%20Design%20Project%20in%20Limassol" class="cta-button">Get Your Free Quote</a>
			</div>

			<a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
